Suggests: libbluray-bdj
Description: Backup BDMV from the command line
 bluraybackup-ex makes a decrypted copy of the whole Blu-ray Disc Movie
 or extracts the main title from a Blu-ray drive, disc image, or BDMV
 directory.
 .
 Inspired by dvdbackup, now maintained as a C17 codebase with modern
 CMake-based builds.
